title: Sono Munou, Jitsu wa Sekai Saikyou no Mahoutsukai: Munou to Sagesumare, Kizokuka kara Oidasareta ga, Gift "Tenseisha" ga Kakusei shite Zense no Nouryoku ga Yomigaetta
altTitle: その無能、実は世界最強の魔法使い　〜無能と蔑まれ、貴族家から追い出されたが、ギフト《転生者》が覚醒して前世の能力が蘇った〜

That Incompetent Is Actually the World's Strongest Wizard - He Was Scorned as Incompetent and Kicked Out of His Aristocratic Family, but His Gift of Reincarnation Awakened and Brought Back the Abilities of His Previous Life
